    # pc "Your auntie is supposed to be coming, but Izzy wanted me to come sit with you until she gets here."
    pc "A vossa tia é suposto vir, mas a Izzy quis que eu viesse ficar convosco até ela chegar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:71
