    # "Older Boy" "That's sis, dummy. That's what her friends call her."
    "Older Boy" "É a mana, tonto. É assim que os amigos dela a chamam."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:73
translate portuguese izzy10_9e4c4b50:

    # "Younger Boy" "Oh yeah!"
    "Younger Boy" "Ah, sim!"

